	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Remitto tibi <persName type="auto_name">Gerionis</persName> et <persName type="auto_name">Fabritii</persName> literas, honorande domine compater, et ago simul magnas gratias pro earum communicatione.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scribitur ex <placeName ref="l1976" cert="high">Augusta</placeName> quoque de caesis pontificiis et Helvetiis auxiliaribus ipsorum.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Fertur item in <placeName type="auto_name">Picardia</placeName> quoque regem 10 amisisse cohortes; itaque novas Helvetiorum copias illuc evocat.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="auto_name">Friburgenses</placeName> hac transituri erant hisce diebus Italiam versus, sed mutato consilio rex in <placeName type="auto_name">Picardiam</placeName> eos festinare iubet.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sic miseri et coeci homines hisce turbis et angustiis se immiscent, quae tandem in ipsorum capita redundant.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Utinam nostri exemplum inde caperent!</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quod <persName type="auto_name">Gallos</persName> nostros attinet, non sine ratione mihi semper suspecti sunt; moliuntur omnino, ut aliquem Buceranismum nobis obtrudant.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Cavendum ergo in tempore.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Si principes nos evocassent ad colloquium, omnino prius nobis conveniendum erat et negotium hoc inter nos ante omnia disceptandum, et hoc ipsi debuerant expectare; nunc suis no praevertunt confessionibus et tanto nos gravant praeiudicio.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><foreign xml:lang="de">Ich bin auch übel mitt inen zfriden,</foreign> nec impune feret <persName ref="p8033" cert="high">Beza</persName>, postquam hoc communiter fuerit cognitum.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ego adhuc silentio omnia premo; metuo etiam novum schisma inter nos; non enim deessent, quibus de veteris contentionis aliquid adhuc adhaeret fermento, qui gaudebunt, si videant suarum obscuritatum se novos habere confessores et defensores.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Consule, quęso, (quid) putes nobis cum <persName ref="p8033" cert="high">Beza</persName> agendum esse.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="de" type="auto">In <placeName ref="l167" cert="high">Genff</placeName> wil es je lenger je böser werden.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="de" type="auto">(Der) präsidennt von <placeName type="auto_name">Camerach</placeName> hatt min herren gewar(net), irthalb guͦt ufsehens zuͦ han; dann si habind etwas verhanden.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Min herren glaubends zum theil, zum theil nüt, und achtet man, man hatzte uns sonst gern an einander.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Der küng hatt in das <placeName type="auto_name">Fustini</placeName> land hinder <placeName type="auto_name">Jonve</placeName> ettliche reisige glegt, frylich uff das zuͦ warten.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Ich sorg übel, es werd nüt guͦts drus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Mitt den unseren, so si gen <placeName ref="l167" cert="high">Genff</placeName> kömmend, darff nieman reden, auch on erlaupnuß deß raths kein gsellschafft halten.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Die <placeName type="auto_name">Frantzosen</placeName> regierend da; die allten burger dörffend sich nüt lan mercken.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Gott well, das es zuͦ guͦtem diene, Amen.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Haec raptim ad tuas.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutant te nostri omnes amantissime.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="24" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernę</placeName>, 20. augusti 1557.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="25" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="auto_name">I. Hall</persName>. tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="26" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro d. Heinrycho Bullingero, Tigurinae ecclesiae pastori fidelissimo, domino et compatri suo colendissimo charissimoque.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
